      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The engine and mechanical systems are functional but show signs of age and significant wear. The exterior paint and body have visible scratches, minor dents, and some fading. The interior upholstery is worn and contains some stains.",
