    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver despite showing its age. While the engine and transmission are functional, you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit loose over bumps. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows clear signs of wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and minor mechanical quirks.",
