    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a vehicle in fair condition that serves as a functional budget-friendly option. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including several scratches, fading paint on the roof, and a few small dings consistent with its age. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and the driver's seat shows significant wear, though all essential electronics remain operational. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely require some maintenance soon to address minor fluid leaks and aging suspension components. It\u2019s a solid project car or a basic commuter for someone willing to put in a little work.",
