      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this masterfully preserved vehicle, currently offered in impeccable showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and showing virtually no signs of previous ownership, this unit represents the pinnacle of its class. Every detail, from the pristine exterior finish to the flawless mechanical synchronization, adheres to the most rigorous standards of excellence. This is a definitive acquisition for the discerning driver who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
